body: "Scope context: The repository lacks an automated npm publishing workflow triggered by version tags. Additionally, Node 24 (current release, will become LTS Oct 2025) is not in the CI matrix. Both are production-readiness requirements for a widely-used npm package.\n\nExecution intent: This chore is tracked under pm-8a2s with component project-management/add-automated-npm-release-workflow-and-node-24-c.\n\nCompletion signal: Pushing a v0.1.0 tag triggers CI + npm publish; Node 24 appears in ci.yml and nightly.yml matrix; docs updated; tests pass at 100%\n\nGovernance intent: Release readiness. Maintain linked files/tests/docs and evidence comments so future agents can reuse this record as authoritative context."
